cs.DL, cs.IR, cs.SI, cs.CL, cs.SD 

This paper discusses the national orientation of scientific journals and their internationalization, which is related to digital libraries (cs.DL), information retrieval (cs.IR), social informatics (cs.SI), computational linguistics (cs.CL), and software development (cs.SD). The paper analyzes the distribution of INO values across disciplines and countries, which is relevant to these sub-categories.
